<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Offer Letter</title>
</head>
<body style="background-color: #f0f0f0; color: #333;">
    <h1>Offer Letter</h1>
    <p>Dear <%= employee.firstname %> <%= employee.lastname %>,</p>
    <p>Congratulations! You have been selected for the role of RPA Developer in our company.
        We are excited to have you on board and look forward to working with you.</p>
    <p>Here are some details about your new role:</p>
    <p>Employee ID: <%= employee.employee_id %></p>
    <p>We are pleased to offer you a position at our company.</p>
    <p>Your Date of Joining is on 10th June 2024.</p>
</body>
</html>
